  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali8-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu collātu piriyaluṟṟa talaivaṉ kuṟippaṟintu tōḻi poruḷatu 
            nilaiyāmai kūṟi avaḷoṭu kūṭic celkiṉṟa ilvāḻkkaic celavē poruḷeṉa avaṉ celavaḻuṅkak kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali8">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>naṭuvikan torīi nayaṉillāṉ viṉaivāṅkak</l>
                <l>koṭitōrtta maṉṉavaṉ kōlpōla ñāyiṟu</l>
                <l>kaṭukupu katirmūṭṭik kāyciṉan teṟutali</l>
                <l>ṉuṟalūṟu kamaḻkaṭāt tolkiya veḻilvēḻam</l>
                <l>vaṟaṉuḻu nāñcilpōṉ maruppūṉṟi nilañcēra</l>
                <l>viṟaṉmalai vempiya pōkkaru veñcurañ</l>
                <l>collā tiṟappat tuṇintaṉirk koruporuḷ</l>
                <l>colluva tuṭaiyēṉ kēṇmiṉmaṟ ṟaiiya;</l>
                <l rend="space">vīḻunark kiṟaicciyāy viralkavar picaikkuṅkō</l> <!-- metrical and wordsplit don't match 
                  picaikkuṅkō vs. icaikkum kōl; I don't change this however as this doesn't upset the lines -->
                <l>lēḻuntam payaṉkeṭa viṭainiṉṟa narampaṟūum</l>
                <l>yāḻiṉu nilaiyilāp poruḷaiyu naccupavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">marīittāṅ koṇṭāraik koṇṭakkāṟ pōlātu</l>
                <l>piriyuṅkāṟ piṟareḷḷap pīṭiṉṟip puṟamāṟun</l>
                <l>tiruviṉu nilaiyilāp poruḷaiyu naccupavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">puraitavap payaṉōkkār tammākka muyalvārai</l>
                <l>varaiviṉṟic ceṟumpoḻutiṟ kaṇṇōṭā tuyirvauvu</l>
                <l>maraiciṉu nilaiyilāp poruḷaiyu naccupavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>naccal kūṭātu peruma viccela</l>
                <l>voḻital vēṇṭuval cūḻiṟ paḻiyiṉṟu</l>
                <l>maṉṉavaṉ puṟantara varuvirun tōmpit</l>
                <l>taṉṉakar viḻaiyak kūṭi</l>
                <l>ṉiṉṉuṟal viyaṉmārpa vatumaṉum poruḷē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
